metadata.name: THE CONTROLLER 1/1
metadata.description:
"THE BEAR MARKET RODEO" IS AN HOMAGE TO NEW AND OLD VETERANS EXPERIENCING THE VOLATILE MARKETS OF A NEW FINANCIAL WORLD.   HIGHLIGHTING VARIOUS TYPES OF INDIVIDUALS THAT PARTAKE AS 'ACTORS' IN THE SPACE. THE BITCOIN WILD WEST TROPE HAS BEEN A LONG STANDING TRADITION IN THE CRYPTOCURRENCY SPACE AND THERE IS SOME ULTIMATE TRUTH TO THAT.  HERE, WE REPRESENT THROUGH A FUTURIST LENS AND POSSIBLY REFLECT ON THE QUITE RIDICULOUS EVENTS THAT WE'VE HAD TO CONFRONT IN THE PAST. THE GOOD....THE BAD....AND THE UGLY PARTS OF IT. - ROBNESS V2

PRODUCTION NOTES:  ALL RARITY COUNTS OF THESE WORKS ARE IN THE TITLE(NUMBERED).  THERE ARE GROUPS OF 31, 25, 20, 10, 5, 2 AND 1.
